snippet: After the 9/11 attacks, tens of thousands of young men and women joined the military, heading for the rugged mountains of Afghanistan and dusty deserts of Iraq....

headline.print_headline: As Army Shrinks, Young Officers Being Pushed Out
headline.main: As Army Shrinks, Young Officers Being Pushed Out

lead_paragraph: After the 9/11 attacks, tens of thousands of young men and women joined the military, heading for the rugged mountains of Afghanistan and dusty deserts of Iraq.
